OL,12,     GKeith Brymer Jones and his
OL,13,     Gpartner Marj start ripping out
OL,14,     Grot at the chapel and pitch their
OL,15,     Gplan to turn it into a home,
OL,16,     Gpottery studio and events space
OL,17,     Gto the local community.
